Description: RxNorm provides normalized names for clinical drugs and links its names to many of the drug vocabularies commonly used in pharmacy management and drug interaction software.Notes on accessbility:* Example URI does not return RDF. Needs to go through a describe.* Download of zip needs authentication (NLM license: https://uts.nlm.nih.gov/license.html)
